      • newAssociate

        public E newAssociate(T owner,
             ViewEntity associateEntity)
               throws Exception
        Creates an instance of type E and populates it using the state of the given view entity.

        This implementation constructs an instance of type E using the no-arg constructor and populates its properties by injecting them using ViewEntity.inject(Object).

        Specified by:
        newAssociate in interface AssociationManager<T,E>
        Parameters:

        associateEntity - a view entity representing the state of the associate in the view
        Returns:
